msgid ""
"Jacques finds himself on a small island, but with no promised riches in "
"sight."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: A_Rough_Life/scenarios/01_Led_Astray.cfg:259
msgid ""
"Shielding his eyes from the evening sun he scans the coast for the hapless "
"ship. He spots smaller boats coming ashore, and suddenly facts click into "
"place. He has been tricked, and an unfortunate fate awaits him!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: A_Rough_Life/scenarios/01_Led_Astray.cfg:264
msgid ""
"He sees not one or two, but four encampments! There's a band of goblin "
"traders who must have masterminded the plot. There are the villagers who "
"tricked him with their rumors, and some farmers who confirmed the shipwreck "
"also in on the scam. Finally, an infestation of mud slime has developed on "
"the island, but that doesn't worry him. What worries him is: traders... and "
"traitors - slime, the lot of them."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Evil Goblin Trader
#: A_Rough_Life/scenarios/01_Led_Astray.cfg:271
msgid ""
"Remember, dere's a good price for each one taken! You may beat 'em "
"senseless, but do not waste 'em. A bonus for dey snotty liddle leader! He "
"will fetch a handsome sum!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Greedy Villager
#: A_Rough_Life/scenarios/01_Led_Astray.cfg:275
msgid "Money! Gimme money!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Greedy Farmer
#: A_Rough_Life/scenarios/01_Led_Astray.cfg:279
msgid "Yes, money, and good riddance to ruffian scum!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Mud Slime
#: A_Rough_Life/scenarios/01_Led_Astray.cfg:283
msgid "Gurgle! (Food!)"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Greedy Farmer
#: A_Rough_Life/scenarios/01_Led_Astray.cfg:287
msgid "Oh no! Slime! Get rid of it, before it finds its way to our shores!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Goblin Handler Jabb
#: A_Rough_Life/scenarios/01_Led_Astray.cfg:291
msgid ""
"Don't forget de grand prize, peasants! De liddle thieves is what we're "
"after. Don't bother with slime rubbish!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Mud Slime
#: A_Rough_Life/scenarios/01_Led_Astray.cfg:296
msgid "Mrrrmm! (Hungry!)."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Jacques
#: A_Rough_Life/scenarios/01_Led_Astray.cfg:300
msgid ""
"I'm not the thief here! But we'll steal your senses with our clubs, you "
"filthy goblins!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Evil Goblin Trader
#: A_Rough_Life/scenarios/01_Led_Astray.cfg:309
msgid ""
"Jabb! Are you sure our rookie troops can control dees pesky ruffians? We "
"could call more experienced mercenaries to wrap dis up quickly."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Goblin Handler Jabb
#: A_Rough_Life/scenarios/01_Led_Astray.cfg:313
msgid ""
"No need, boss! Dees punching bags are easily dealt with. We could squash 'em "
"like bugs."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Jacques
#: A_Rough_Life/scenarios/01_Led_Astray.cfg:317
msgid "I'm mightily tempted to squash you, goblin!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Goblin Handler Jabb
#: A_Rough_Life/scenarios/01_Led_Astray.cfg:321
msgid "Come and get me!"
msgstr ""

#. [objective]: condition=win
#: A_Rough_Life/scenarios/01_Led_Astray.cfg:326
msgid "Jacques resists capture for at least 15 turns"
msgstr ""

#. [objective]: condition=lose
#: A_Rough_Life/scenarios/01_Led_Astray.cfg:330
msgid "Jacques is captured before turn 15"
msgstr ""

#. [note]
#: A_Rough_Life/scenarios/01_Led_Astray.cfg:338
msgid ""
"There is a special bonus for Jacques if he kills the Goblin Handler Jabb"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Goblin Handler Jabb
#: A_Rough_Life/scenarios/01_Led_Astray.cfg:347
msgid "No slacking, boys, go get 'em!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Goblin Handler Jabb
#: A_Rough_Life/scenarios/01_Led_Astray.cfg:355
msgid ""
"Faster, men, faster! You're not going to let 'em escape so easily, are you?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Greedy Farmer
#: A_Rough_Life/scenarios/01_Led_Astray.cfg:364
msgid "Ahh, shut up!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Greedy Farmer
#: A_Rough_Life/scenarios/01_Led_Astray.cfg:370
msgid ""
"I have to say that Goblin Handler was a tough fighter, but it's nice and "
"quiet without him."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: A_Rough_Life/scenarios/01_Led_Astray.cfg:391
msgid ""
"Observing the enemy, Jacques sees a pattern in the goblin handler's "
"movements. He hangs back, the coward, but now and then rushes in to yell "
"commands to his troops."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: A_Rough_Life/scenarios/01_Led_Astray.cfg:396
msgid ""
"Perhaps if Jacques times it correctly, he can bushwhack the handler without "
"exposing himself to the enemy camps."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Goblin Handler Jabb
#: A_Rough_Life/scenarios/01_Led_Astray.cfg:411
msgid ""
"You can run, twist and dodge all you want, but you will never escape us! The "
"villagers want you gone, and we want de gold!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Jacques
#: A_Rough_Life/scenarios/01_Led_Astray.cfg:415
msgid "Like you said yourself a while ago: Come and get me!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Jacques
#: A_Rough_Life/scenarios/01_Led_Astray.cfg:423
msgid ""
"Whatever happens, at least now I have proven my worth in cuts and bruises "
"and may hold my head high."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Evil Goblin Trader
#: A_Rough_Life/scenarios/01_Led_Astray.cfg:436
msgid "Jabb! <i>Dey'll be easy pickings</i>, you said."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Goblin Handler Jabb
#: A_Rough_Life/scenarios/01_Led_Astray.cfg:440
msgid "Well, boss, dey should be easy to beat. Dey're almost as small as us!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Evil Goblin Trader
#: A_Rough_Life/scenarios/01_Led_Astray.cfg:444
msgid ""
"You idiot! Can't you see it's taking much too long to overcome 'em? Forget "
"it! It's time to bring in de big guys."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Goblin Handler Jabb
#: A_Rough_Life/scenarios/01_Led_Astray.cfg:449
msgid "Ok, boss."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Evil Goblin Trader
#: A_Rough_Life/scenarios/01_Led_Astray.cfg:455
msgid ""
"Dis is tougher den I thought. I don't care what my arrogant handler said "
"before - call in de heavy cavalry!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Greedy Farmer
#: A_Rough_Life/scenarios/01_Led_Astray.cfg:471
msgid "We've had enough. Let's go home, boys!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Greedy Villager
#: A_Rough_Life/scenarios/01_Led_Astray.cfg:479
msgid "Fall back, lads! Let the big guns take care of it."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Goblin Handler Jabb
#: A_Rough_Life/scenarios/01_Led_Astray.cfg:493
msgid "Goblins! To me! Protect your leader!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Goblin Handler Jabb
#: A_Rough_Life/scenarios/01_Led_Astray.cfg:504
msgid "You dare sneak around me? Men, come and help me get dis one chained up!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: A_Rough_Life/scenarios/01_Led_Astray.cfg:525
msgid "Let me bust dis slime for you amateurs!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=second_unit
#: A_Rough_Life/scenarios/01_Led_Astray.cfg:550
msgid "What's dis gob of slime doing? Is it really attacking me? Help, help!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=second_unit
#: A_Rough_Life/scenarios/01_Led_Astray.cfg:561
msgid "Hey! Dis thing can attack! Help, help!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: A_Rough_Life/scenarios/01_Led_Astray.cfg:589
msgid "I can't believe I'm killed by a stupid slime! Ahh..."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Goblin Handler Jabb
#: A_Rough_Life/scenarios/01_Led_Astray.cfg:604
msgid "Did you see, men? Dat's how you tether a restless calf!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Jacques
#: A_Rough_Life/scenarios/01_Led_Astray.cfg:621
msgid "Gotcha! Not so smug now, are you?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Goblin Handler Jabb
#: A_Rough_Life/scenarios/01_Led_Astray.cfg:626
msgid "Wha-? How did you manage to sneak up on me? Dat was..."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Goblin Handler Jabb
#: A_Rough_Life/scenarios/01_Led_Astray.cfg:632
msgid "How could dis happen to me? Gone forever..."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Jacques
#: A_Rough_Life/scenarios/01_Led_Astray.cfg:636
msgid "Well, he didn't die at my hand, but at least we got rid of him."
msgstr ""

#. [floating_text]
#: A_Rough_Life/scenarios/01_Led_Astray.cfg:667
msgid "<span color='green'>+1 melee attack</span>"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Jacques
#: A_Rough_Life/scenarios/01_Led_Astray.cfg:672
msgid "Good riddance. Hehe, this sword feels good in my hand!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: A_Rough_Life/scenarios/01_Led_Astray.cfg:683
#: A_Rough_Life/scenarios/02_Captivity.cfg:268
#: A_Rough_Life/scenarios/04_Unrest_in_the_Ranks.cfg:222
msgid "Aaaargh!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Evil Goblin Trader
#: A_Rough_Life/scenarios/01_Led_Astray.cfg:693
msgid ""
"Ahh! Not as springy as I thought. No auction for him den, just de gallows..."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Evil Goblin Trader
#: A_Rough_Life/scenarios/01_Led_Astray.cfg:702
msgid ""
"Ahh, a feisty little character, indeed! Dat'll do nicely for where I am "
"about to send him..."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Evil Goblin Trader
#: A_Rough_Life/scenarios/01_Led_Astray.cfg:730
msgid "How can dis be? And with my retirement villa just one venture away..."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: A_Rough_Life/scenarios/01_Led_Astray.cfg:734
msgid ""
"Against all odds, the goblin trader boss is slain. Yet the others finally "
"overcome the proud young thief..."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Jacques
#: A_Rough_Life/scenarios/01_Led_Astray.cfg:743
msgid ""
"Ha! The dragon may take me, but its head's cut off just the same! Never will "
"my own head drop like that in disgrace."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: A_Rough_Life/scenarios/01_Led_Astray.cfg:762
msgid ""
"Jacques perseveres for days, but at last they overcome him. Fear's in their "
"eyes, yes, and a gleam of anticipation. For such a sturdy fighter brought to "
"auction in the Wild Plains will be... profitable."
msgstr ""

